&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&quot;Up and Out&quot; Navigation:&lt;/strong&gt; Teach sellers how to move from a technical user base to the CIO/CDO office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SaaS Sales Math:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide expertise in managing by the numbers and maintaining deep proficiency in Salesforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Land and Expand Mechanics:&lt;/strong&gt; Share proven strategies for increasing Net Revenue Retention (NRR) year-over-year.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
